* [[Robert E. Harrist Jr.]]: A scholar's landscape: Shan-chuang t'u by Li Kung-lin, Princeton University, 1989
* Elizabeth Chipman Brotherton: Li Kung-lin and long handscroll illustrations of T'ao Ch'ien's "Returning Home", Princeton University, 1992
* Anyi Pan: Li Gonglin's Buddhist beliefs and his "Lotus Society Picture": An iconographic diagram of the bodhisattva path. University of Kansas, 1997
